name: Air Canada 787-8 Dreamliner [C-GHPT] Evening Arrival at Toronto Pearson ᴴᴰ
description:
As usual, a great flight with Air Canada! Here we have AC's second Dreamliner delivered, C-GHPT Fin 802 arriving at Toronto Pearson International Airport on runway 23, literally two days after I had spotted there! You can see the "bird's nest", as YYZ spotters affectionately call it, that I spotted from right on final. Video log below if you want to skip to any certain parts. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

VIDEO LOG:
06:00 - Spoilers extended.
09:10 - Banking to join downwind for runway 23.
10:00 - A great view of the airport.
11:15 - Close up shot of downtown Toronto!
12:10 - Turning base for 23.
14:10 - Flaps extending
18:45 - On final for 23.
19:15 - Passing the "bird's nest", where all my YYZ videos were filmed.
19:35 - Touchdown!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
